Package com.dua3.utility.logging.log4j

Class LogAppenderLog4j.LogEntryDispatcherLog4J

java.lang.Object
com.dua3.utility.logging.log4j.LogAppenderLog4j.LogEntryDispatcherLog4J
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogEntryDispatcher
Enclosing class:
LogAppenderLog4j
public class LogAppenderLog4j.LogEntryDispatcherLog4J extends Object implements LogEntryDispatcher
This class represents an implementation of the LogEntryDispatcher interface using Log4J. It dispatches log entries to registered handlers based on a filter.
